description: This file is the entry point for a React web application. It imports React, ReactDOM, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component, then renders the App component inside the element with id 'root' using React.StrictMode for extra checks.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering React components into a DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the DOM within the created React root.
